new_weapon

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
new_weapon -  This method setups the weapon with the new condition.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void new_weapon(int new_condition)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^new_condition%^RESET%^ - the condition value of the weapon

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/weapon.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method setups the weapon with the new condition.  It sets the
maximum and lowest conditions to the specified condition.
.EP

